        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">1. WireGuard: The Modern Standard</h2>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-50 to-blue-50 border-2 border-green-500 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="text-5xl">‚ö°</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Why WireGuard is Taking Over</h3>
