                Released in 2020, WireGuard has become the go-to protocol for modern VPNs. It's faster, more secure, and simpler than older protocols‚Äîrepresenting the biggest leap in VPN technology in 20 years.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Technical Specs</h3>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
