            <li><strong>Authentication:</strong> Poly1305 for message authentication</li>
            <li><strong>Key Exchange:</strong> Curve25519 (elliptic curve Diffie-Hellman)</li>
            <li><strong>Hashing:</strong> BLAKE2s and SipHash</li>
            <li><strong>Code Size:</strong> ~4,000 lines vs. 400,000+ for OpenVPN</li>
            <li><strong>Platform Support:</strong> Built into Linux kernel 5.6+, available for Windows, macOS, iOS, Android</li>
