          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            <li>‚Ä¢ You're in a country that blocks WireGuard (China, Russia)</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ You need maximum compatibility with older devices/routers</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ You want to disguise VPN traffic as HTTPS (port 443 TCP)</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Your VPN provider doesn't support WireGuard yet</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
