      <section id="avoid" class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">4. Protocols to Avoid (PPTP, L2TP)</h2>

        <div class="bg-red-50 border-2 border-red-500 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="text-5xl">‚ö†Ô∏è</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-900 mb-2">Do Not Use These Protocols</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                PPTP and L2TP/IPSec are outdated, insecure, and should never be used for privacy. If your VPN only offers these, switch providers immediately.
              </p>
            </div>
